== Latin ==

=== Suffix ===
'''-issimus -issima -issimum'''
# added to adjectives to form [[superlative]]

=== Usage notes ===
Adjectives that end in ''-er'' instead take the suffix ''[[-rimus]]'' (e.g. ''[[liber]]'' -&gt; ''[[liberrimus]]'').
The superlative of ''[[bonus]]'' is ''[[optimus]]''.

